com.slightech.ble.mynt

类 MyntListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.slightech.ble.mynt.MyntListener
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    com.slightech.ble.mynt.MyntIntent

    public class MyntListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.slightech.ble.mynt.MyntIntent
    zh:

    监听设备连接配对、状态变化、读写事件回调

    设备事件监听有两只方式可以实现： 方式一：直接在MyntMnager设置回调监听接口。 方式二：注册MyntListener 调用 调用register 开启监听，unregister 停止监听。并且需要调用 MyntMnager的 setCallbackBroadcast(true) MyntListener 才能接收到事件回调。

    en:

    Monitor device connection, status change, read and write event callback

    There are two ways to realize the device event monitoring: way: directly in the MyntMnager to set up the callback listener interface. mode two: MyntListener call call call register to open the listener, unregister stop monitoring. And need to call MyntMnager setCallbackBroadcast (true) MyntListener to receive the event callback.
